1.2.name: wordpress/accelerate-your-advertising
1.2.description: faq,demo,idea,or suppert:http://chinainvestor.net/accelerate-your-advertising Many webmaster wonder why their web site is so slowly? OK, the reason is slow advertising code from some AD union. Now,I write a wordpress plugin which can accelerate your advertising and speed your site. You can choose to make these slow advertising code be shown after the appearance of the content.
